<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久很久以前，有一个叫杰克的男孩儿和他的妈妈住在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克不是很聪明，但是他心地善良，也很勤奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，杰克在小河边的一家磨坊里辛勤地工作着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>作为报酬，他得到了两个银币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回家路上，杰克玩儿着银币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他被一颗石头绊倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！啊，我的钱！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是已经太迟了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>扑通， 扑通！两枚银币先后掉进了小河里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克回到家，他的妈妈很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下次记得把你的报酬放进口袋里！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，妈妈。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久之后，杰克在一家面包店里辛勤地工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>作为报酬他得到了一条面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回家的路上，他按照妈妈说的话，把面包放进了口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到家后，杰克马上跑向妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，看！这次我把报酬放进口袋里了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克把面包从口袋里拉了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀，面包被挤碎了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，下次记得把报酬放在头顶上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈告诉他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久之后，杰克在一个农场里工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他工作非常努力，作为报酬最后得到了一罐儿牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得照妈妈说的，把这罐牛奶顶在头上。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克小心地把牛奶顶在了头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他努力保持着平衡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是杰克需要经过一棵满是枝干的大树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他头顶的牛奶碰到了一根树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克回到家后，难过得几乎要哭了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，别难过。下次记得把报酬扛在肩膀上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，妈妈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久之后，杰克在集市上非常努力地工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>集市主人很满意，作为报酬给了他一头驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一次，我要把驴扛在肩膀上！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样我就可以把它安全地带回家了。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是驴太重了，杰克连走路都很困难。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎哟，好重的驴呀！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为了转移注意力，杰克开始唱一首好笑的歌儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘟嘟嘟嘟！嘟嘟嘟嘟！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>驴也因为不舒服而叫喊着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯昂！嗯昂！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克努力不让驴掉下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没有看到正在路旁野餐的国王和公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主看到杰克歪歪扭扭地走在路上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>听到他和驴发出的好笑的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈哈！这是我见过的最好笑的事情！”她大笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，女儿笑了。”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她终于笑了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>自从公主的母亲去世后，公主就没有笑过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也从来没有人能让她笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王看到公主笑了，开心极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把杰克叫了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子！你让我女儿笑了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请你做我女儿的丈夫吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克跪了下来，“陛下，谢谢您！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和他的妈妈去了城堡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和公主结婚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们幸福地生活在了一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈哈！嘟嘟嘟嘟！嘟嘟嘟嘟！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>